{
  "modifications": [
    "1. Once upon a time, in a cheerful town, Jack found his dream job and met the love of his life, Emily.",
    "2. Jack's company downsized; he lost his job but kept supporting his family by working long night shifts.",
    "3. Sadly, Emily fell ill with no sign of recovery; Jack sold everything they had to afford her medical bills.",
    "4. Jack grieved as Emily passed away, leaving him broken and alone in their now-empty house."
  ]
}
